Arnold Stang https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arnold_Stang 0 Arnold Stang (September 28, 1918 – December 20, 2009) was an American comic actor and voice actor, whose comic persona was a small and bespectacled, yet brash and knowing big-city type.
